<plot>Lester, a skinny kid lives with his rat in an abandoned car underneath the freeway overpass. On this epic journey he makes friends with dead fish, chases Waldo around a Spaghetti O's can, finds guidance in the gutter and meets our country-fried president. His hallucinations, dreams and fragmented half-truths go full circle when he returns home to his Starsky &amp; Hutch styled 71 Ford Torino.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?570703</url></doc>
